ChangeLog of Serotonina - A Simple C++ Artificial Neural Network Library

============= Serotonina 1.1.4 - urgency=low =============

2011-06-20  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Added some generic methods.

============= Serotonina 1.1.3 - urgency=low =============

2011-06-19  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * synapse.hpp: Removed `TrainData`.

    * trainer.hpp: Removed `Trainer->CreateTrainData` and `Trainer->DeleteTrainData`.

    * train-algorithm.cpp: Added `TrainAlgorithm->AllocData` and `TrainAlgorithm->DeallocData`.

    * network.hpp, trainer.hpp: Added generic methods.

============= Serotonina 1.1.2 - urgency=medium =============

2011-06-17  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Now training algorithms are classes: `train-algorithm.hpp`.
           Updated all examples to version 1.1.2 .

    * trainer.hpp: `Trainer->Train` and `Trainer->TrainOnFile` are again template functions. -_-"

    * network.hpp: Now `Network` uses `std::vector`.
                   Added `Network->GetOutputs()`.

============= Serotonina 1.1.1 - urgency=medium =============

2011-06-17  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Updated `CMakeLists.txt`
           Added `CMakeLists.txt` to compile examples.
           Added `FindSerotonina.cmake`.
           Updated all examples to version 1.1.1 .

    * trainer.hpp: Now `Trainer->Train` and `Trainer->TrainOnFile` are non-template functions.

    * network.hpp: Fixed data hiding of `Network` class.

============= Serotonina 1.1.0 - urgency=medium =============

2011-06-15  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Deleted `network-train.cpp` and created `Trainer` class to training neural network.
           Now Serotonina is extensible!
           Updated all examples to version 1.1.0 .

    * network.hpp: Added `Network->MakeStructures`.
                   Added new `Network` constructors.

============= Serotonina 1.0.7 - urgency=medium =============

2011-06-14  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Split `network.cpp` into `types.hpp`, `macros.hpp`, `string.hpp`, `neuron.hpp`, `synapse.hpp`, and `layer.hpp`.
           Merged `LayerConnections` to `Layer` structure.
           Removed Serotonina's namespace from `st_gym`, `st_ocr`, and `st_face_recognition` examples.

    * network.cpp: Moved `Network->training_report` to `network-train.cpp`. 

============= Serotonina 1.0.6 - urgency=low =============

2011-06-12  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Fixed printf format of `size_t`.
           Now the compiler flags are `-Wall -ansi -pedantic -pedantic-errors`.
           Added `serotonina/types.hpp` header.

    * st_ocr: Added `Gym->CommandLine` function (to finish).

    * CMakeList.txt: Now you can compile Serotonina without dipendencies.

============= Serotonina 1.0.5 - urgency=low =============

2011-06-10  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

	* all: Improved performance!! ;)

    * network-train.cpp: Added elapsed time of training.

    * network-train.cpp (function `Network->BackpropagateError`): Fixed stupid nested loop.

============= Serotonina 1.0.4 - urgency=low =============

2011-06-05  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Added `examples/face.cpp`.

    * network-train.cpp (function `Network->ComputeError`): Removed unused iterator `size_t j`.

    * CMakeList.txt: Fixed `serotonina.hpp` installer.

============= Serotonina 1.0.3 - urgency=medium =============

2011-06-02  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Split `network.cpp` into `network-train.cpp`.

    * network.cpp (function `Network->Run`): Added network's input validation.

    * network-train.cpp: Added `Network->CreateTrainData()` and `Network->DeleteTrainData()`
                         methods to dynamic memory management during training.

=============== Serotonina 1.0.2 - urgency=low ===============

2011-06-02  Wicker25  < wicker25@gmail.com >

    * all: Added this ChangeLog file to the project.
           Added main header file for easy importing `include/serotonina.hpp`.

